                android:text="Collect paper, plastic, polyethylene and glass separately and bring to Zipple (Malakan Park, 043409090) or (ZAKIAN 10 ONLY PAPER , 091913536).
You know  that only together we can begin sorting and recycling our waste bin. Paper, plastic, glass ...
